features: ☆Safe Healthy Fabrication Technique: Squeeze feeding spoon is made of food-grade silicone to protect baby from chemical risks. PPSU material prevents food leakage problems. Pacifier is made of food grade materials and stable PP. Tiny holes prevents choking and suffocation. Manufactured by ultrasonic Lace Machine, the sturdy structure makes you believe it is safe in the hands of infants

☆Thermal Safety Indication: When food is placed on the green side of the baby spoon and the temperature of the food is higher than 38°C, the green color will slowly change to white, which is a hot warning. Let food and fruit be eaten at the right temperature

☆Different Types and Sizes Available: A utensil set of spoons, squeeze feeders, pacifiers. There are three sizes of pacifiers: S, M, L. For Reference: S for 3-6 months infant, M for 6-12 months toddler, L for 12-24 months babe

☆Precise and Comfortable Use: The silicone bottle with scale ensures accurate amount of food, and its cap can be used as an upright abutment. All products can be washed and sterilized in 100℃ boiling water, it is recommended not to exceed 3 minutes

☆One for a Gift or a Nice Kit: A beautiful package contains 11 pieces of feeding utensils. Available for daily feeding, chewing fruit, continuous feeding, grain feeding, drink feeding and other occasions. Exquisite outer packaging and cute product design make the whole product lovely

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Lictin Baby Food Feeder Pacifier Set Feeding Supplies 11 Pcs

Safe Pacifier 2MM Tiny holes create juicy feeling, eliminating the possibility of choking and suffocation. Cut food or fruit into small pieces and put them in the pacifier. The ring-shaped grip is convenient for the baby to grasp. The natural silicone material is harmless to the baby and will not be broken during the bite. Easy Clean All items can be washed and cleaned in boiling water. It is recommended not to exceed 3 minutes. When boiling and sterilizing, please ensure that the temperature is within the heat-resistant temperature range. Hot-safe baby spoons cannot be disinfected frequently at high temperatures. Dust Proof When not in use, the cover and cap can relieve your worries about dust and dirt. Excellent air tightness prevents dust and dirt from falling on the feeding place of the pacifier and spoon. Place it after cleaning, if you need to use it, you can take it out at any time.

The hot-safe spoon can be used flexibly in many situations. The pacifier is suitable for a variety of fresh fruits and vegetables. Silicone baby spoon is suitable for breast milk, formula milk or fruit puree.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for starting solids
reviews.reviewText: I really like all the pieces in this kit. The silicone squeeze spoon has a questionable shape, me and my husband had a good laugh about it when I pulled it out of the box. The only thing, I wish the squeeze spoon had a flat bottom where the food goes in so it stands upright with the spoon facing up. It comes with a stopper to separate the food/spoon halves though so it doesn’t leak. Very happy with this purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 1, 2021
reviews.reviewText: Love the value. What you get is definitely great for the price. The only issues I have is that the silicone feeder does leak with the cap on it and they do stain very easily. My personal experience was with any baby food with a yellow or orange tint. However, the hard plastic on the spoons does detect heat very well compared to other products of its kind so it's a give and take in that situation. Overall a great set for teething babies or a momma on the go. Just a side note, the rubber on the teething binkies is very thin so if your little one already has a few pearly whites they will rip through it so be mindful.

reviews.reviewText: I used the same type of spoons with my twins' nephews, It was so handful and easy to feed two at one time. This one has a lid for the spoon so the spoon can stand by itself. Also, those fruit rings are awesome my son loves eating out of them. Regular spoons are so soft and great for the little ones it will never hurt their soft jaws.

This set is cool. The large container is particularly handy for babies who want to eat themselves. And the spoon attached to the end minimizes mess. At first, I was unsure how to keep it stand while it is opened, but then I figured out that it needs to be placed in the lid. :) The quality is also very good.

Los pedí ya que mi niña no podía lograr la ke tomara agua y con el biberón cuchara lo pude lograr, los chupones para fruta no los use así que no tengo un cometario. Preferible que mi bebé coma si frutita directamente de su mano a la boca

En conjunto lo recomiendo ampliamente, este producto me ha servido mucho para ahorrarme tiempo y esfuerzo para darle de comer a mi bebe sus papillas y comida en general, lo que mas utilizo es la cuchara rellenable que es sin duda algo que me dejo sorprendido por la facilidad con la que puedes darle de comer en tan poco tiempo.La razón por la que no le doy 5 estrellas es por que el plástico con el tiempo se mancha, en especial con la zanahoria y queda de un color naranjado y no hay manera de quitarlo, como que el plástico no es de la mejor calidad pero que mas se puede pedir por el precio y la cantidad de accesorios que vienen incluidos.
